Progress App
This line optimizes the site depending on the device (mobile, tablet or desktop).
This line of code must be found in the index.html file at the head.
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
also in the public folder next to index.html we must find a manifest.json file.
to work progress app we need the serviceWorker.js file
https://github.com/jeffposnick/create-react-pwa/compare/starting-point...pwa


